name: ☾ WM'S VIRTUE
description:
BE FREE. let the wind blow through your body. travel the unknown. be the one you need for yourself. bind yourself to your self through your art, a natural expression of the appreciation of life within you.
Description pyrite and quarts beads all hung on aluminium chain, with antique gold plated earring clasp. Earrings are 10cm in length. All applicable taxes included.

name: ☾ FATE
description:
the only one who could break my heart did. LOST. to cling so tightly to someone who never truly cared. to let go and to try again. FOUND. to make mistakes for a reason. only time will show you how.
Description Pyrite, quarts, agate, aluminium and silver plated beads pendant all hung on aluminium chain. One of a kind.
Chain is 70cm in length. All applicable taxes included.

name: ☾ ADEY
description:
Stands straight and tall. Dances fearlessly. Smiles carefully. Moves elegantly. A flower with the deepest roots
Description Tooth shaped howlite beads, pyrite beads, and aluminium findings all hung on antique gold aluminium chain.
Necklace is 35cm in length. All applicable taxes included.

name: ☾ BLAK SAND
description:
blak sand. a lie is not a lie if you mean it at the time. it came to me in a dream that it would be time to let you fly. I hold only my spirit hand, connect me to the moon, and I see more with my eyes closed than when they are open. the real truth is in intuition.
Description Black onyx beads, silver plated links hung on aluminium chain.
Necklace is 40cm in lenth (at its lowest point) All applicable taxes included.

name: ☾ GLORY

triumph - hard work - tears - emotion - reasoning - understanding - love - appreciation - pride - recognition

Chain is 70cm in length. All applicable taxes included.

name: ☾ NOVEMBER
description:
I told her my favourite number is 8 because that is the day she was born. this time, she turned 22. birth month 11 twice. I like that. she grows with me.
Description agate crystal adorned with aluminium plated beads and aluminium chain. All applicable taxes included.

name: ☾ DAFAR

All applicable taxes included.

description:
someone told me loving yourself prevents sickness. time to work through the shame and fear. we all deserve the best love from ourselves.

All applicable taxes included.

name: ☾ MERO
description:
I stand at your edge. Waves crashed on your shores for millennia and will for long after I am gone. Wonder. I wish to imprint you with my presence for more than a moment. Show you, show the universe I am worthy or remembrance, evidence of my existence. Footprints in the sand, waves promptly wash them away.
Description Pendant made of pyrite bead and aluminium chain all hung on aluminium chain. Available in 70cm chain length. All applicable taxes included. *No individual piece is exactly the same due to the uniqueness of the materials used.

honour your art, its your souls way out.

description:

Description coral and black plastic and aluminium beads, with aluminum chains on an antique gold earring clasp.
